videos.description: Cory Alexander and Mike Couzens break down Pittsburgh's win against Syracuse and discuss the remaining challenges Pittsburgh has this season.
videos.headline: Great second half leads to Pittsburgh win

videos.description: Winning on the road in the ACC is never easy, and Pittsburgh celebrates after holding Syracuse to a 37 percent shooting from the field in their 66-52 win.
